articles.title: Australia's Boxing Day Test victory seals series against Pakistan - ICC Cricket
articles.description: Australia overcame an improved Pakistan side at the MCG to win the Boxing Day Test on the eve of the fourth day’s play and gained crucial ICC World Test Championship points.
